dct_title_s: Уканїна оґладоба мапа : мирyло 1:1 000 000 / Мапа ; мапу укладено та пидхотовлено до друку МП "Мапа ЛТД" за уцхастиу Українського Аерохеодезнчно г; редактор Ю Лоза.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading and spot heights. Includes: six ancillary maps:  "Iz istoriï ukraïnsʹkoï derz︠h︡avnosti," showing the territorial historical evolution from the 12th century to 1920. Also shows county-level (rayon) administrative divisions and forests. Accompanied by text/index: Poi︠a︡sni︠u︡valʹnyĭ tekst. 44 p. ; 29 cm. Includes notes, table of no. of local administrative divisions, and key to abbreviations. "Zamovlenni︠a︡ no. 325."
